1.00	Ultradrug	Ultradrug	Ultradrug is a compilation of material from the Psychic TV albums Ultrahouse The L.A. Connection and Ultrahouse The Twelve Inch Mixes. The album is composed of new edits of the tracks from both releases. It was reissued in 1999 as the second CD of the compilation "Origin Of The Species" Volume Too!, with one track differing. See also Sirens (Ultradrug - Thee Sequel).	
